Name: Restored "Music Sheet"
AttributesDescription: A "music sheet" marked with the notes restored by the Soliskin.
BgDescription: Beginning, climax, finale... red, yellow, and green marks rest quietly in order, forming a complete score. These colors once drifted separately, carried by wind, water, and light. until they return to a single melody. It is a song they completed together. And it remains, even now, a gentle echo that the Soliskin still remember.
ObtainedShowDescription: A "music sheet" recovered by the Soliskin. It records the complete Melody Matthew taught them.
